\
	%!TEX encoding =\
	%!TEX root =\
	%!TEX TS-program =\
	%!TEX projectfile = \
\
allow a space between % and ! for better formatting, and to remove %! postscript ambiguity. The old syntax without the space is, of course, also supported.\
\
